Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.90,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嘘か夢か
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.90,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失うのは身体と
