Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.90,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是夢是幻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.90,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失去的是身體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:52.47,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和自我之心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:54.26,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}付出如此代價
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.33,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又能得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:01.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}連這淚水都能將之奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:04.41,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生命脆弱而飄忽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.88,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}當一切造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.03,0:01:11.21,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要將死亡歎作恐怖嗎
